###

` HELM INIT CHART

helm create demo-project

` HELM EXPORT NAMESPACE IN OPENSHIFT

set TILLER_NAMESPACE=edb-cources

or in linux

export TILLER_NAMESPACE=edb-cources

` HELM INSTALL CHART TO OPENSHIFT

helm install --name demo-test demo-project

` HELM LIST OUR APPS IN OPENSHIFT IN OUR NAMESPACE

helm list

` HELM DELETE CONFIG FROM OPENSHIFT

helm delete --purge demo-test